写的拙劣的文字。 他们能生成符合自己口味的东西，我为他们感到开心。但我也会忍不住的想，我会不会再也没有一百个读者了。 ——— 以下都是deepseek生成的文章。"},"attached_info":"CkII57j/yffL7NEBEAMaCTExMzEyNDUwMiDB8OC8BjAAOOQBQB1yCzEwNzQxMzg0NjA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-b2d4712d5e5ab37e8efbe5e5c6330675_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2025-02-23 16:20:56"}}